{"type": "article", "id": 24829, "title": "彩色方形糖包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-01T06:54:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 89, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607164750awqAVr8QzxjLY5bM.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这组糖果包装来自意大利的一家巧克力品牌 SABADÌ，6种不同颜色的方形糖作为“脸”，被覆上了生动的表情。包装分为罐装和纸袋装两种，纸袋子画有一个摆了“pose”的糖果，上飘荡着对应颜色的水果和叶子，是非常清新的插画风格。罐子上的“糖果”三个为一组踢球、跳绳，每一面都不一样，完全可以做送礼的纪念品。<a href=\"http://www.happycentro.it/sabadi_le_caramelle/\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607164747h3NGtzAfbQa0piDj.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.608\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607164748vEuBZT7gWVz2Fhp3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071647486fhEtu0P3jXGRaOH.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.608\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071647497pjLhGCoyVH38z0W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607164749uY1faLWOKXMAUC2T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071647501YsZ5QNzHVvPqr6M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}